          <title>Padres muster no offense to support Yu Darvish's inspired pitching in NLDS loss to Dodgers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES (AP) — Yu Darvish tapped the “PS” patch on his uniform and then went to work on the way to an inspired performance. Yet, try as he might, Darvish’s stellar outing in memory of late San Diego Padres owner Peter Seidler was not enough to overcome the Los Angeles Dodgers on Friday night.]]></description>
